{"tid":2019603,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"遊行男子涉丟煙頭　隨時被判監","createTime":"2020-05-16T11:44:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T08:50:46.000Z","uid":37554,"like":2,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"170e47bc1431b817a3dfe179d4e6102bbd2156a0","tid":2019603,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T11:44:07.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】去年12月1日「毋忘初心」反修例遊行，隊頭抵紅磡後爆警民衝突。其間一名男子被指在警員面前丟煙頭，並曾拒出示身份證，被控在公眾地方亂拋廢料及抗拒警員兩罪。亂拋垃圾一般以定額罰款處理，但本案動用刑事控罪，最高可判監三個月。有大律師直指除非涉大量或重複拋垃圾，否則刑事起訴實屬浪費公帑，「法庭真係冇咁多時間做咁大量瑣碎無聊嘅案件！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200516/6MUK5L6RNAFVZ44DMN2YDMY2CI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200516%2F6MUK5L6RNAFVZ44DMN2YDMY2CI%2F&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2Bb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=2ae1c65b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200516%2F6MUK5L6RNAFVZ44DMN2YDMY2CI%2F&h=d2344f12\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200516/6MUK5L6RNAFVZ44DMN2YDMY2CI/</a>"},{"pid":"f32343e6651991f05b2b6a7ea64e4d0e99a0649d","tid":2019603,"uid":43041,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T11:59:43.000Z","msg":"借位求救<br />\n<br />\n前蓋式洗衣機有咩推薦？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2019609\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2019609</a>"},{"pid":"8b54915c9ad73ac52313350f1bc179c7ae5161e8","tid":2019603,"uid":15605,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T12:03:45.000Z","msg":"遲啲喺班狗面前呼吸都要判監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb48bd710f99e5ef84e846b7960f259302e13c2","tid":2019603,"uid":181502,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"8b54915c9ad73ac52313350f1bc179c7ae5161e8","tid":2019603,"uid":15605,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T12:03:45.000Z","msg":"遲啲喺班狗面前呼吸都要判監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T12